Uses of Package
items

  • Packages that use items 
    Package Description
    gameengine
    This package serves as a medium to connect the backend interface to the front end GUI.
    gui
    This package consits of all the different GUI windows that the game contains
    items
    This package provides Items namely FoodItems and Medicine
    planet
    This contains all the planets used in the game
    units
    this package contains unit classes that make up the crew in the game, such as Crew, CrewMember and different CrewMember types.
  • Classes in items used by gameengine 
    Class Description
    Items
    The super class to all the food, medicine, money and spaceship parts in the game.
  • Classes in items used by gui 
    Class Description
    Items
    The super class to all the food, medicine, money and spaceship parts in the game.
  • Classes in items used by items 
    Class Description
    FoodItems
    The super class of all the food types available in the game.

    Medicine
    The super class to all the different medicines in the game.
  • Classes in items used by planet 
    Class Description
    AlienGrubs
    AlienGrubs is an object of food type Alien Grubs which costs 60 dollars and reduces hunger by 45 points.
    CalceraPhos400
    CalceraPhos400 is an object of CalceraPhos400 medicine type, which costs 50 dollars and increases health by 50 points
    Items
    The super class to all the food, medicine, money and spaceship parts in the game.
    KalaxianCrystals
    KalaxianCrystals is an object of CalceraPhos400 medicine type, which costs 50 dollars and decreases hunger by 40 points
    Money
    class dedicated to the money attribute of the crew.
    NeutrinoBombs
    NeutrinoBombs is an object of NeutrinoBombs medicine type, which costs 100 dollars and decreases hunger by 70 points.
    NZT48

    Popplers
    Popplers is an object of NeutrinoBombs medicine type, which costs 25 dollars and decreases hunger by 20 points
    R89
    R89 is an object of CalceraPhos400 medicine type, which costs 60 dollars and increases health by 70 points
    Spaceettios
    Spaceettios is an object of NeutrinoBombs medicine type, which costs 70 dollars and decreases hunger by 50 points.
    SpaceshipPart
    class dedicated to the number of space ship parts found attribute of the Crew class.
    StrawberrySmiggles
    StrawberrySmiggles is an object of NeutrinoBombs medicine type, which costs 30 dollars and decreases hunger by 25 points
